a10e00e58e7c1909b61bd4e.mp4?t=1743167282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>• You will find your favorite characters, such as Getafix, Cacofonix and Vitalstatistix, as well as new characters with hilarious names! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1109690/extras/82f7c1ac4da7162b23cdfef3f4ed990f.poster.avif?t=1743167282\" width=624 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1109690/extras/82f7c1ac4da7162b23cdfef3f4ed990f.webm?t=1743167282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1109690/extras/82f7c1ac4da7162b23cdfef3f4ed990f.mp4?t=1743167282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>• Complete various side missions and collect hidden objects on all levels.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1109690/extras/7920b64f00929b3063b19d7b07652663.poster.avif?t=1743167282\" width=624 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1109690/extras/7920b64f00929b3063b19d7b07652663.webm?t=1743167282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1109690/extras/7920b64f00929b3063b19d7b07652663.mp4?t=1743167282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
